-- BNDES Will Boost Infrastructure Funding Further, Guimaraes Says
-- B y   B o r i s   K o r b y   a n d   G a b r i e l l e   C o p p o l a
-- 2012-06-06T15:15:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-06/bndes-will-boost-infrastructure-funding-further-guimaraes-says.html
Brazil ’s state development bank will
increase lending for infrastructure after doubling it to more
than 40 percent of all disbursements, according to Sergio Foldes
Guimaraes, deputy managing director of the international
division of what is known as BNDES.  “A huge pipeline of investments will come to BNDES in new
sectors, like airports for instance,” Guimaraes said yesterday
in an interview from Bloomberg’s headquarters in  New York .
“Infrastructure is really a priority for us.”  To contact the reporters on this story:
